ZH: 这场灾难造成了数百人无家可归。
EN: This disaster has left hundreds of people homeless.

ZH: 灾难过后，我们必须团结起来恢复家园。
EN: After the disaster, we must come together to rebuild our homes.

ZH: 这场火灾是一场人类历史上最严重的灾难之一。
EN: The fire is one of the most severe disasters in human history.

ZH: 他们的灾难来临时，我们必须伸出援手。
EN: We must extend a helping hand when their disaster strikes.

ZH: 政府正在全力应对这场自然灾难。
EN: The government is working hard to respond to this natural disaster.

ZH: 灾难可能会给我们带来很多伤痛和损失。
EN: Disasters may bring us much pain and loss.

ZH: 只有团结一心，我们才能战胜这场灾难。
EN: Only by uniting can we overcome this disaster.

ZH: 灾难的影响会持续很长时间。
EN: The impact of the disaster will last for a long time.

ZH: 他们必须在最短的时间内从这场灾难中恢复过来。
EN: They must recover from this disaster as quickly as possible.

ZH: 灾难之后，我们必须加强防灾和救助措施。
EN: After the disaster, we must strengthen disaster prevention and relief measures.

ZH: 这类灾难对当地经济产生了重大影响。
EN: This type of disaster has had a significant impact on the local economy.

ZH: 我们必须汲取教训，以减少未来可能发生的灾难。
EN: We must learn from this disaster to reduce the likelihood of future ones.

ZH: 灾难的根源在于人类对自然的不尊重。
EN: The root cause of the disaster lies in human disrespect for nature.

ZH: 她的家人在那场灾难中失去了一切。
EN: Her family lost everything in that disaster.

ZH: 灾难纪念日是用来纪念那些在灾难中失去生命的人们。
EN: Disaster memorial day is to remember those who lost their lives in the disaster.

ZH: 他们的生命在那场灾难中被永远改变。
EN: Their lives were forever changed by that disaster.

ZH: 这场灾难给我们敲响了警钟，我们必须警惕不再重蹈覆辙。
EN: The disaster has sounded the alarm for us, and we must be vigilant to avoid repeating the same mistakes.

ZH: 尽管受灾较重，但大家仍然团结一心，共同渡过难关。
EN: Despite the heavy disaster, everyone still united and overcome the difficulties together.

ZH: 灾难的到来唤起了人们对生命的珍视。
EN: The arrival of the disaster has awakened people's cherishing of life.
